OL,3,CHot Cross Bun heads home - seal badly
OL,4,Churt by fishing net returns to the wild
OL,6,FA seal pup that was badly injured by a
OL,7,Ffishing net has been returned to the
OL,8,Fwild, as the Cornish Seal Sanctuary
OL,9,Furges the government to take action on
OL,10,Fbycatch.
OL,12,FHot Cross Bun was rescued on 10 April
OL,13,Ffrom Nanjizal Bay near Penzance after
OL,14,Fmembers of the public found him
OL,15,Ftangled up in rope netting.
OL,17,FVolunteer marine mammal medics from
OL,18,FBritish Divers Marine Life Rescue
OL,19,Fmanaged to remove the net and bring
OL,20,Fthe pup to the Cornish Seal Sanctuary.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
