FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781963310
OL,3,CHot Cross Bun heads home - seal badly
OL,4,Churt by fishing net returns to the wild
OL,6,FWhen he arrived in Gweek, vets at the
OL,7,Fsanctuary found the netting had caused
OL,8,Fwide, deep wounds across the back of
OL,9,Fhis neck.
OL,11,FAlthough his injuries were severe, Hot
OL,12,FCross Bun has recovered well.
OL,14,FStaff at the sanctuary cleaned and
OL,15,Ftreated his wounds daily, and within a
OL,16,Fweek they were showing signs of
OL,17,Fhealing.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781963310
OL,3,CHot Cross Bun heads home - seal badly
OL,4,Churt by fishing net returns to the wild
OL,6,FAfter three weeks, he had progressed
OL,7,Ffrom the hospital unit to the
OL,8,Frehabilitation pools, where time in
OL,9,Fsaltwater helped his recovery.
OL,11,FHot Cross Bun was released on 10 June
OL,12,Falongside his pool-mate Churro. He
OL,13,Fweighed a healthy 36kg and bore only
OL,14,Fsome scarring as a lasting reminder of
OL,15,Fhis ordeal.
OL,17,FHis was the final release of the
OL,18,Fsanctuary's 2025`2026 rehabilitation
OL,19,Fseason.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
