OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781963310
OL,3,CHot Cross Bun heads home - seal badly
OL,4,Churt by fishing net returns to the wild
OL,6,FGrace Jones, conservation coordinator
OL,7,Fat the Cornish Seal Sanctuary, said:
OL,8,F"Watching Hot Cross Bun return to the
OL,9,Fwild is a reminder of both the
OL,10,Fresilience of marine wildlife and the
OL,11,Fchallenges it faces.
OL,13,F"While his story has a happy ending,
OL,14,Fmany animals are not so lucky.
OL,15,FReducing bycatch is one of the most
OL,16,Fimportant steps we can take to better
OL,17,Fprotect our marine and coastal
OL,18,Fspecies."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
