PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781963310
OL,3,CHot Cross Bun heads home - seal badly
OL,4,Churt by fishing net returns to the wild
OL,6,FDefra has previously told ITV News it
OL,7,Fis committed to "restoring our oceans
OL,8,Fto good health" and "taking action to
OL,9,Freduce the bycatch of marine species" .
OL,11,F"Our flagship programme Clean Catch
OL,12,Fuses electronic monitoring to collect
OL,13,Fbycatch data and evaluate the
OL,14,Feffectiveness of mitigation measures,
OL,15,Fand our new Seabird Bycatch Action
OL,16,FPlan will look to reduce seabird
OL,17,Fdeaths in and around English waters,"
OL,18,Fa spokesperson said.
OL,20,F'Incredibly rewarding' to see marine
OL,21,Fmammals recover and return to the wild
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
