OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781963310
OL,3,CHot Cross Bun heads home - seal badly
OL,4,Churt by fishing net returns to the wild
OL,6,FStaff at the sanctuary say it has been
OL,7,Fa demanding season for them.
OL,9,FThey treated 47 rescued pups, 72.3% of
OL,10,Fwhich were wounded, with others
OL,11,Farriving malnourished or suffering
OL,12,Ffrom respiratory conditions.
OL,14,FThe team got through 8,000kg of fish,
OL,15,F658 towels, and 10,150 wellington boot
OL,16,Fchanges along the way.
OL,18,FCream Puff was another of the season's
OL,19,Fmemorable cases. She was a white-coat
OL,20,Fpup rescued at just one day old and
OL,21,Fthe youngest admitted this season.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781963310
OL,3,CHot Cross Bun heads home - seal badly
OL,4,Churt by fishing net returns to the wild
OL,6,FShe needed tube feeding and assisted
OL,7,Ffeeding for more than two months
OL,8,Fbefore gradually learning to feed by
OL,9,Fherself.
OL,11,FIn the end she spent six months in
OL,12,Fcare before her release in March 2026.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, Abeona underwent surgery to
OL,15,Fremove an eye damaged in a suspected
OL,16,Fentanglement. She recovered so well
OL,17,Fshe was released just two months after
OL,18,Fher operation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781963310
OL,3,CHot Cross Bun heads home - seal badly
OL,4,Churt by fishing net returns to the wild
OL,6,FBethan, an animal care specialist at
OL,7,Fthe sanctuary, said:"Every seal pup
OL,8,Fthat comes through our doors has a
OL,9,Funique story, and this season has
OL,10,Fcertainly kept us on our toes.
OL,12,F"From tiny pups requiring round-the-
OL,13,Fclock feeds to complex medical cases
OL,14,Flike Hot Cross Bun and Abeona, it's
OL,15,Fbeen incredibly rewarding to watch
OL,16,Fthese animals recover and return to
OL,17,Fthe wild where they belong."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
